videos.description: LeBron James acknowledges Kyle Korver's hot second quarter and Kyrie's clutch fourth quarter as the Cavs finished off a sweep of the Raptors.
videos.headline: LeBron impressed with teammates

videos.description: Demar DeRozan doesn't play the what-if game and doesn't make any excuses after getting swept by the Cavaliers.
